data.value: Pro-Dodger is a game created by us, Farit Ali Zafar and Ahmed Rana . It's a simple yet addictive game. You get to drive a car, dodge obstacles and maneuver moves to keep for self from crashing. It's a very fun game to play and once you start playing it, you won't notice the time fly by, it's just so much fun. The Purpose of making this game is we want to do something different, a game that anyone can play. It will be very simple game but it will be better.
